function
code that repeat instruction when called

argument / parameter
value sent to function when called

arbitrary argument
when you don't know number of argument inside function

recurse function
function can call itself to loop data

scope
where value and function can be accesed

global scope
value / function can be accessed anywhere in program

file or module scope
value / function can only be accessed within file

function scope
value / function only visible within function

code block scope
value / function only visible within { } code block
